article.description: — Jordan Dingle had 24 points as Penn narrowly beat Bucknell 73-68 on Sunday.
article.headline: Dingle scores 24 to lift Penn past Bucknell 73-68
article.linkText: Dingle scores 24 to lift Penn past Bucknell 73-68
article.story: LEWISBURG, Pa. -- — Jordan Dingle had 24 points as Penn narrowly beat Bucknell 73-68 on Sunday. Jelani Williams had 17 points for Penn (1-2). Clark Slajchert added 13 points. Andrew Funk scored a career-high 32 points for the Bison (0-2). Elvin Edmonds IV added 10 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
